### Notification Management Tests

### Get Notifications - Default Pagination
GET http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Get Notifications - Custom Pagination
GET http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/notifications?limit=10&offset=5
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Get Notifications - Count Only
GET http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/notifications?count_only=true
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Mark Notification as Read
PUT http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/notifications/789e0123-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174002/read
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Mark All Notifications as Read
PUT http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

# Example expected response:
# {
#   "message": "All notifications marked as read successfully",
#   "read_notification_ids": [
#     "789e0123-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174002",
#     "789e0123-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174003"
#   ]
# }

###

### Delete Notifications
DELETE http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notification_ids": [
    "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
    "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222"
  ]
}

# Example expected response:
# {
#   "message": "Notifications deleted successfully",
#   "deleted_count": 2,
#   "deleted_notification_ids": [
#     "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
#     "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222"
#   ]
# }
#
# Status codes:
# - 200: All notifications deleted successfully
# - 206: Partial success (some notifications not found)
# - 404: No notifications found

